    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it is honestly such a gem. It\u2019s been well-loved and is in really solid shape, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or those fun weekend getaways! It drives smoothly and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019ve taken great care of this car and I\u2019m looking for someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
