    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S features the high-revving 3.8L M97 flat-six, delivering 355 hp through a tactile G97 6-speed manual transaxle. Equipped with PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) for adaptive damping and a factory short-shift kit, the mechanical feedback is exceptional. The chassis remains taut with refreshed control arm bushings, and the naturally aspirated power delivery remains linear and visceral. Meticulously maintained with documented oil analysis and recent bore scoping to ensure internal integrity, this is a turn-key driver for the purist seeking a refined, analog experience.",
